treiber auseinandergesetzt. Wie kann zukünftiges Wachstum entstehen? Die Studie legt dar, inwiefern das Innovationspotenzial der Hotellerie im Geschäftsfeld Vertrieb und Marketing Wachstumsauslöser der Branche werden kann.  aThe German hotel market is among Europe’s largest and most attractive markets, but it has shown little growth in sales in recent decades. How can we ensure future growth? Until now, the hotel industry has had little involvement in innovation to drive growth. The study describes ways to harness the innovation potential of the hotel industry in sales and marketing as a stimulant for growth.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aHotel management. 4aHospitality. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Management.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1z978311076249508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2016z9783110485158oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831104489240 cprintz978311044880140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311045143640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110451436423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110451436/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-076249-5  DG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DBVb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016